1
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:42,060
=Twin Fire Dawn=

2
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:45,060
=Episode 29=

3
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:11,760
You've never forgotten her.

4
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:14,200
And you've never truly loved me.

5
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:15,640
Not even for a moment.

6
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:20,560
I'm sorry, Xue Wan.

7
00:01:21,080 --> 00:01:22,640
I'm very grateful you saved my life.

8
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:24,520
But you know it too.

9
00:01:25,640 --> 00:01:26,600
When it comes to you...

10
00:01:28,360 --> 00:01:30,320
I've always understood it clearly.

11
00:01:30,520 --> 00:01:31,920
You never truly loved me.

12
00:01:32,520 --> 00:01:35,200
And actually, I didn't
love you that much either.

13
00:01:35,840 --> 00:01:38,360
So I came today to tell you something.

14
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:39,960
With the war lately,

15
00:01:40,320 --> 00:01:42,760
my brother has decided
to move the whole family abroad.

16
00:01:43,240 --> 00:01:45,519
The Xue family
did so much for me before,

17
00:01:45,520 --> 00:01:47,920
yet I did nothing in return.

18
00:01:48,240 --> 00:01:51,560
I've decided to go abroad
with my brother and help him.

19
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:53,000
You're leaving?

20
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:54,800
Mm.

21
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:58,560
So today I want
to say something honestly.

22
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:01,520
You don't need to feel guilty toward me.

23
00:02:01,800 --> 00:02:03,160
Actually, I realized long ago

24
00:02:03,350 --> 00:02:05,400
that what I felt for you
was more admiration than love.

25
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:07,120
I helped you return to Yancheng

26
00:02:07,240 --> 00:02:08,640
and become Commander-in-Chief

27
00:02:08,680 --> 00:02:10,719
only because when you
were Commander of Yancheng,

28
00:02:10,720 --> 00:02:12,880
it was a blessing
for all the people of Yancheng.

29
00:02:12,920 --> 00:02:15,360
And that had nothing to do with love.

30
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:19,120
I respect your decision.

31
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:21,520
You're a good woman
who cares about the world.

32
00:02:22,160 --> 00:02:23,360
You deserve someone better.

33
00:02:24,880 --> 00:02:25,800
Thank you.

34
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:28,440
Today, even though
I knew your intentions,

35
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:30,560
I still went along with this act.

36
00:02:31,040 --> 00:02:32,359
Because only this way

37
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:34,360
could I see your gentleness toward me.

38
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:36,240
Sometimes I wonder

39
00:02:36,920 --> 00:02:38,280
if without her,

40
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:40,520
I wouldn't have become who I am today.

41
00:02:41,080 --> 00:02:42,079
But when I saw today

42
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:43,640
what you did to her,

43
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:45,280
I felt terrible inside.

44
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:47,240
I thought I hated her.

45
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:49,480
Hated her for taking my identity
and marrying you.

46
00:02:49,600 --> 00:02:50,839
But when I tortured her,

47
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:52,239
I realized I wasn't happy at all.

48
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:54,120
I believe you're the same.

49
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:56,760
You're speaking for her?

50
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:00,840
I'm just saying what's truly on my mind.

51
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:04,520
Actually, Zhuang Yunqiu
never truly hurt you.

52
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:08,000
Everything between you
was only a misunderstanding.

53
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:10,480
But it's different for me.

54
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:12,920
She personally

55
00:03:13,920 --> 00:03:15,880
said those hurtful words to me

56
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:18,200
and personally shot me.

57
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,600
But you survived, didn't you?

58
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:24,440
Maybe there's
another side to this matter.

59
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:29,880
Anyway, we've known
each other for some time.

60
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,600
I hope everything
goes well for both of you.

61
00:03:32,900 --> 00:03:34,499
And I hope everything
goes well for you too.

62
00:03:37,600 --> 00:03:38,560
Then I'm leaving.

63
00:04:27,280 --> 00:04:28,039
Someone.

64
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:29,280
Prepare the car to the hospital!

65
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:42,800
The Commander's wife
really has a hard life.

66
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:46,520
What do you mean?

67
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:50,199
Not only does
the Commander treat Madam badly,

68
00:04:50,200 --> 00:04:51,600
he treats the child badly too.

69
00:04:51,760 --> 00:04:53,719
The Commander often hits the child.

70
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:55,119
One time when they were arguing,

71
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:56,000
I overheard it.

72
00:04:56,200 --> 00:04:58,680
This child isn't the Commander's.

73
00:04:58,880 --> 00:05:00,559
And for some reason,

74
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:02,479
the Commander kept telling Xiaoxiao

75
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:04,920
that this child wasn't
born in the Bingchen year.

76
00:05:05,440 --> 00:05:07,080
Not born in the Bingchen year?

77
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:08,880
Then when was she born?

78
00:05:09,440 --> 00:05:10,640
Get me her medical records.

79
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:11,199
This...

80
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:11,800
What?

81
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:14,520
Fine.

82
00:05:45,640 --> 00:05:46,440
Commander.

83
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:48,200
Here.

84
00:05:51,320 --> 00:05:52,479
(The First Army Hospital of Yancheng)

85
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:54,200
(Zhuang Xiaoxiao.
Date of Birth: May 29th, Yimao Year)

86
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:59,080
May 29th, Yimao Year?

87
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:10,880
Xiaoxiao wasn't born
in the Bingchen year.

88
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:16,840
(Reason for hospitalization: Malnutrition,
frequent dizziness, bruises found on the body...)

89
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:19,240
She's my child.

90
00:06:22,840 --> 00:06:25,239
(It was to protect our child)

91
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:27,160
(that you suffered so much.)

92
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:28,959
(And I...)

93
00:06:28,960 --> 00:06:30,720
(I misunderstood you all this time.)

94
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:33,520
(Don't worry.)

95
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,560
(I'll save her.)

96
00:06:57,840 --> 00:06:58,720
Eat.

97
00:07:25,760 --> 00:07:26,760
Follow him.

98
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:28,680
Don't alert him.

99
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:35,000
Gu Shaoyan.

100
00:07:35,080 --> 00:07:37,240
(Only this way can I find Xiaoxiao.)

101
00:07:45,280 --> 00:07:46,400
Xiaoxiao.

102
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:55,600
(This...)

103
00:07:56,280 --> 00:07:57,920
(Could he already know?)

104
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:09,360
- Madam.
- Where's the Commander-in-Chief?

105
00:08:09,440 --> 00:08:10,400
Where is he?

106
00:08:14,280 --> 00:08:14,959
Commander.

107
00:08:14,960 --> 00:08:16,760
Where's Xiaoxiao?

108
00:08:16,880 --> 00:08:18,279
She's my last bargaining chip now.

109
00:08:18,280 --> 00:08:19,800
Bring her to me.

110
00:08:20,320 --> 00:08:21,320
Commander.

111
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:23,440
Xiaoxiao is gone.

112
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:24,520
What?

113
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:26,399
Commander.

114
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:29,039
Let me help you escape. I've arranged a car.
I can get you out of here.

115
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:29,520
Com...

116
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:30,400
Commander.

117
00:08:33,280 --> 00:08:36,200
You can't even handle
something this simple.

118
00:08:43,040 --> 00:08:44,520
Lu Shaoyuan.

119
00:08:45,040 --> 00:08:46,120
Gu Shaoyan.

120
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:48,600
Stop struggling like a trapped beast.

121
00:08:49,800 --> 00:08:51,280
I checked the hospital records.

122
00:08:51,920 --> 00:08:53,280
Xiaoxiao is my daughter.

123
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:54,680
Lu Shaoyuan!

124
00:08:55,800 --> 00:08:58,000
Zhuang Yunqiu and I
were together for six years.

125
00:08:58,520 --> 00:09:00,640
Six whole years,
and I still couldn't have her.

126
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,440
And now,

127
00:09:02,920 --> 00:09:05,000
she's going to be with you too.

128
00:09:07,880 --> 00:09:10,440
I will never let
your family get what you want.

129
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:12,480
Never!

130
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:14,800
Hand over Xiaoxiao,

131
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:16,760
and I'll spare you.

132
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:19,520
Lu Shaoyuan.

133
00:09:20,160 --> 00:09:21,440
Then kill me.

134
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,800
I've spent my whole life

135
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:29,480
living in your shadow.

136
00:09:30,160 --> 00:09:31,679
I'm never going
to let you have your way.

137
00:09:31,680 --> 00:09:32,880
It was me

138
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:34,800
who made you look so high and mighty.

139
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:38,640
As long as I die,

140
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:41,360
you'll never find Xiaoxiao.

141
00:09:47,160 --> 00:09:51,850
♪How can broken love ever go on?♪

142
00:09:53,160 --> 00:09:58,480
♪How much hope must fade into despair?♪

143
00:09:58,980 --> 00:10:02,560
♪In the blink of an eye,
everything falls apart♪

144
00:10:02,900 --> 00:10:05,910
♪Bound by the fate we cannot escape♪

145
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:11,200
♪You and I caught in
this tangled love and hate♪

146
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:17,510
♪Fragile hearts can hardly bear goodbye♪

147
00:10:18,570 --> 00:10:24,170
♪How many times
must pain cut deep before we wake?♪

148
00:10:24,710 --> 00:10:28,090
♪I once gave myself
to you so completely♪

149
00:10:28,340 --> 00:10:31,289
♪Still holding on to that heart♪

150
00:10:31,290 --> 00:10:36,429
♪Only to suffer your fatal blow♪

151
00:10:36,430 --> 00:10:40,749
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

152
00:10:40,750 --> 00:10:43,329
♪Yet I approach you with such caution♪

153
00:10:43,330 --> 00:10:45,609
♪How could a stand in ever have♪

154
00:10:45,610 --> 00:10:49,159
♪The right to be loved by you?♪

155
00:10:49,160 --> 00:10:53,689
♪If love is nothing
more than endless schemes♪

156
00:10:53,690 --> 00:10:56,220
♪Used and abandoned in the end♪

157
00:10:56,360 --> 00:10:58,309
♪Still I walk into♪

158
00:10:58,310 --> 00:11:01,909
♪The trap you set without regret♪

159
00:11:01,910 --> 00:11:05,959
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

160
00:11:05,960 --> 00:11:08,539
♪Yet keep it buried deep inside♪

161
00:11:08,540 --> 00:11:10,699
♪A stand in can never cross♪

162
00:11:10,700 --> 00:11:14,139
♪The shortest distance between us♪

163
00:11:14,140 --> 00:11:19,110
♪If love can
make someone lose themselves♪

164
00:11:19,270 --> 00:11:23,940
♪Then let me stay by your side♪

165
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:28,289
♪A substitute♪

166
00:11:28,290 --> 00:11:33,290
♪Needs no reason♪

